2026-05-16T23:27:48.6890805Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-16T23:27:48.6891668Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-16T23:27:48.6892556Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-16T23:27:48.6893572Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-16T23:27:48.6894893Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-16T23:27:48.6895909Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-16T23:27:48.6930073Z 33    -->
