2026-05-16T23:27:49.0805509Z 273            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-16T23:27:49.0805847Z 274            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-16T23:27:49.0806058Z 275            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-16T23:27:49.0806743Z 276            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-16T23:27:49.0807091Z 277            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-16T23:27:49.0807416Z 278            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
